Module fi.tuni.prog3.weatherapp

module fi.tuni.prog3.weatherapp
Defines a Java module for the WeatherApp application. Specifies required dependencies and access rules for the modules. This module integrates JavaFX for GUI functionality, uses FXML for defining the UI, and requires the com.google.gson library for JSON processing. It opens the package fi.tuni.prog3.weatherapp to allow access to the FXML components. The module exports fi.tuni.prog3.weatherapp to make it accessible to other modules.
